    {
      "card": {
        "bgColor": "var(--gray-3)",
        "label": "Lesson 3 • Discussing a new ad campaign",
        "descriptions": [
          {
            "description": [
              {
                "text": "Ted works for an advertising agency. He’s presenting to Sam and Lisa, who work for Pacific Beer Company."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Lisa: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Ted would like to "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"run some"
            },
            {
              "text":	" ideas by us for our new ad campaign."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Ted: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Please "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"keep an open mind"
            },
            {
              "text":	". Remember that "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"nothing is set in stone"
            },
            {
              "text":	" yet. We’re still just"
            },
            {
              "markedText":	" brainstorming."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Sam: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I hope that doesn’t mean we’re about to hear a lot of "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"half-baked ideas"
            },
            {
              "text":	"!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Ted: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I think you’re going to like this. Our idea is to use a black bear as our mascot.* Our "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"tagline"
            },
            {
              "text":	" can be: “Strong enough to satisfy a bear.”"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Lisa: "
            },
            {
              "text": "It would be great if people would associate our brand with a bear — strong and independent. That would really improve our brand equity. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Sam: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I don’t want to "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"throw cold water on"
            },
            {
              "text":	" your idea, but where did you get the idea for a bear?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Ted: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Didn’t you hear about that bear at the campground a couple weeks ago? He entered a tent and drank two dozen Pacific beers! What a great endorsement for Pacific beer! "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Lisa: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I think we’re "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"on the right track"
            },
            {
              "text":	" with this campaign. The bear should "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"generate lots of buzz"
            },
            {
              "text":	". Everybody will be talking about the bear who loves Pacific beer!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Ted: "
            },
            {
              "text": "And here’s the "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"icing on the cake"
            },
            {
              "text":	": he won’t demand an "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"arm and a leg"
            },
            {
              "text":	" to "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"plug our product"
            },
            {
              "text":	". In fact, we can probably pay him in beer!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Sam: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Okay, you’ve "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"twisted my arm"
            },
            {
              "text":	". Let’s "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	" run with the idea."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Ted: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Great. I’ll "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"flesh it out"
            },
            {
              "text":	" some more and "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"touch base"
            },
            {
              "text":	" with you in a couple of days."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
